<section class="container-xl text-center">
  <div class="">
    <h1 id="siteTitleBannerText">MeowWoof</h1>
    <p class="siteBannerText">
      Completing Families Since 2022
    </p>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="img-fluid">
  <img
    src="/images/homepage_banner_.jpg"
    alt="Group of adorable dogs and cats"
    id="homeBanner"
  />
</section>

<section class="container-xl text-center bg-light siteBannerTextAlternate">
  <div>
    <h2 class="pt-4" id="siteSubheaderBannerText">
      ü¶¥ Our Mission ü¶¥
    </h2>
    <p class="py-4">
      ‚ÄúMeowWoof provides care, comfort and compassion to animals in need while engaging the hearts, hands and minds of our community to bring about an end to abandoned and orphaned shelter animals. All lives are precious and we will continue to do our part to fortify that belief.‚Äù
